  "text": "In order to quantify the geographic variations of the receipt of breast cancer treatment, whether the receipt of treatment varies significantly across census tracts, the median odds ratio (MOR) was estimated in this study [CITATION_1] . A larger MOR indicates a larger geographic variation and there is no geographic variation if the MOR is 1. More details about MOR can be found elsewhere [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
